Package ics202.project.edges

Edges used to construct different types of graphs

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEdge<VType>
    The base edge for all edges.
    DirectedEdge<VType>
    An edge that has only one direction.
    DirectedWeightedEdge<VType>
    An edge that has weight and direction.
    UndirectedEdge<VType>
    A simple edge with no direction or weight.
    UndirectedWeightedEdge<VType>
    This class represents an edge that has only weight.
